snippet.title: The Nefargad Gameplay Trailer #TheNefargad
snippet.description:
The Nefargad is a thriller, horror, puzzle, and storytelling game that offers a true first-person perspective. The game narrates the story of an archaeologist named Mert, who is kidnapped and imprisoned in a dungeon and his efforts to escape.

The Nefargad Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/27...

Oriseus Studios: https://www.oriseus.com
